<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>À Louer : <%= property.title %></title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans']">

    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto bg-white min-h-screen shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-64 bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-white">
            <span class="text-4xl">🏠</span>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1120]"><%= property.title %></h1>
                    <p class="text-slate-500"><%= property.address %>, <%= property.commune %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#F59E0B] text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm">
                    <%= property.price.toLocaleString('fr-FR') %> FCFA
                </div>
            </div>

            <hr class="my-6 border-slate-100">

            <h2 class="font-bold mb-4">Postuler pour ce logement</h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">Déposez votre dossier en 30 secondes. Notre IA analyse votre solvabilité instantanément.</p>

            <form action="/apply/<%= property.id %>" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-1">Votre Nom Complet</label>
                    <input type="text" name="name" required class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-xl p-3 focus:border-[#F59E0B] outline-none">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-1">Téléphone</label>
                    <input type="tel" name="phone" required class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-xl p-3 focus:border-[#F59E0B] outline-none">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-1">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" name="email" required class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-xl p-3 focus:border-[#F59E0B] outline-none">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-1">Revenus Mensuels (Salaires + Primes)</label>
                    <input type="number" name="income" required placeholder="Ex: 450000" class="w-full border border-slate-300 rounded-xl p-3 focus:border-[#F59E0B] outline-none">
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1">Sera vérifié via relevés Mobile Money ou bulletins.</p>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-[#0B1120] text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl mt-4 hover:bg-slate-800 transition">
                    Vérifier mon éligibilité
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
